{"tid":1392033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日幫老母開咗fb","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T10:38:20.000Z","uid":281492,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9cd28bd71e48c65f085d6e3f0e68abb91fdbe2","tid":1392033,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"老母廿幾三十年前申請單程證嚟香港<br />\n本身係中立嚟 但唔多like大陸<br />\n612嗰日睇到啲狗開槍<br />\n就幫手買物資俾我收工拎過去<br />\n仲攞埋波鞋、長遮同背囊俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（我愛老母！）<br />\n之後一直都係淺黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日佢叫我幫佢開fb嗰陣<br />\n順手幫佢like埋立場、蘋果、612等等嘅page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢而家開始攞啲post嚟同我哋幾兄弟姊妹討論啦<br />\n全家變深黃指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5338c4ad4fc9e3d2b57b454a83e097594aab5d","tid":1392033,"uid":268106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"記得有啲要block啦"},{"pid":"6f70615fe53585fd7e417e970c84b8ce2ec05fb4","tid":1392033,"uid":281492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb5338c4ad4fc9e3d2b57b454a83e097594aab5d","tid":1392033,"uid":268106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"記得有啲要block啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一陣間返去幫佢block先"}]}